    Text: The reading is done, dear, but one thread is still pulling at you... Are
      you afraid?
  - Speaker: Madame Lichenia
    Text: There is an antiquarian with a blue atlas hidden beneath his counter. It
      might interest you.
  choices:
  - choiceText: Huh? An atlas? Like a geography one? OK imma talk to him
